title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Red Bull Air Race - Silverstone F1 track
description:
Welcome to the Red Bull Air Race at the Silverstone F1 racing track. In this video we will look at a cool new addon which has been released for MSFS 2020 which can be used in combination with the Silverstone F1 track which was released a while ago. We are going to fly in style using a Red Bull livery for the Extra 330LT airplane.

The addons in this video can be downloaded from the links below:

Red Bull Air race:
https://flightsim.to/file/22731/red-bull-air-race-silverstone-circuit-event

Silverstone Motorsport Circuit UK & Heliport EGBV 
https://flightsim.to/file/17999/wip-silverstone-motorsport-circuit-uk

EXTRA330 HA-PET - Red Bull Mobile Livery (Peter Besenyei)
https://flightsim.to/file/12251/extra330-ha-pet-red-bull-mobile-livery-peter-besenyei
